985).<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.discogs.com/Stephen-Sondheim-Follies-In-Concert/release/9932587|title=Stephen Sondheim - Follies In Concert|website=Discogs|language=en|access-date=2019-08-17}}</ref>  Label:  [[RCA Records|RCA]].  LP, CD, Digital.\n* [[Sherry!|Sherry! The Broadway Musical]] - Studio Cast (2004).<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.discogs.com/Various-Sherry-The-Broadway-Musical-World-Premiere-Cast-Recording/release/11671419|title=Various - Sherry! The Broadway Musical (World Premiere Cast Recording)|website=Discogs|language=en|access-date=2019-08-17}}</ref>  Label:  Angel Records.  CD, Digital.\n* [[Annie (musical)#Recordings|Annie - The Broadway Musical 30th Anniversary Production]] - Various Artists (2008).<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.discogs.com/Various-Annie-The-Broadway-Musical-World-Premiere-Complete-Recording-30th-Anniversary-Production/release/11035046|title=Various - Annie: The Broadway Musical - World Premiere Complete Recording (30th Anniversary Production)|website=Discogs|language=en|access-date=2019-08-17}}</ref>  Label:  [[Time Life]].  CD, Digital.\n\n==Awards and recognition==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!scope=\"col\" style=\"width:1%;\" | Year\n!scope=\"col\" style=\"width:10%;\" | Award\n!scope=\"col\" style=\"width:20%;\"| Category\n!scope=\"col\" style=\"width:10%;\" | Nominated work\n!scope=\"col\" style=\"width:10%;\" | Role\n!scope=\"col\" style=\"width:5%;\" | Result\n!scope=\"col\" style=\"width:1%;\" class=\"unsortable\"|{{Abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 1962\n| [[Peabody Award]]\n| Personal Award\n| Her comedic performances\n| rowspan=\"4\" | Herself\n| {{won}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.peabodyawards.com/award-profile/personal-award-carol-burnett|title=Personal Award: Carol Burnett|work=[[Peabody Award]]|publisher=[[Henry W. Grady College of Journalism and Mass Communication]]|location=[[Athens, Georgia]]|accessdate=November 1, 2016}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[Primetime Emmy Award]]\n| ro